     If your character loses an arm, he will attack and cast spells much more slowly. A character loses an arm when the arm's health reaches 0. You can see this in the Information window if it's switched to "Hit locations" mode.

     If your character has lost a leg, his/her movement will be much slower. A character loses a leg when the leg's health falls to 0. You can see this in the Information window if it's switched to "Hit locations" mode.
